OL,3,CSuspended MP to be sentenced for
OL,4,Cpunching man in street
OL,6,FAn MP suspended for punching a man
OL,7,Ffollowing a row in the street is set
OL,8,Fto be sentenced.
OL,10,FMike Amesbury, who represents Runcorn
OL,11,Fand Helsby, has been sitting as an
OL,12,Findependent since he was suspended
OL,13,Ffrom the Labour Party following his
OL,14,Farrest in October 2024.
OL,16,FHe pleaded guilty at a hearing in
OL,17,FJanuary to assaulting 45-year-old Paul
OL,18,FFellows in Main Street in Frodsham,
OL,19,FCheshire, in the early hours of 26
OL,20,FOctober, and will now be sentenced at
OL,21,FChester Magistrates' Court.
