OL,6,FThe court heard Amesbury had been
OL,7,Fdrinking before he arrived at a taxi
OL,8,Frank, where Mr Fellows approached him
OL,9,Fto remonstrate about a bridge closure
OL,10,Fin the town.
OL,12,FCCTV footage showed Labour MP Mike
OL,13,FAmesbury assaulting a man in the
OL,14,Fstreet.
OL,16,FFootage showed Amesbury punch Mr
OL,17,FFellows to the head, knocking him to
OL,18,Fthe ground, then follow him onto the
OL,19,Froad and start to punch him again, at
OL,20,Fleast five times.
