OL,6,FHe was then heard saying "you won't
OL,7,Fthreaten your MP again will you?"
OL,9,FThe court heard the sentencing
OL,10,Fguidelines for the offence ranged from
OL,11,Fa high level community order up to a
OL,12,Fprison sentence.
OL,14,FDistrict Judge Tan Ikram told Amesbury
OL,15,Fhe was "leaving all options open at
OL,16,Fthis stage".
OL,18,FSpeaking outside court after entering
OL,19,Fhis guilty plea, Amesbury said: "I'm
OL,20,Fsincerely sorry to Mr Fellows and his
OL,21,Ffamily."
