OL,4,Cpunching man in street
OL,6,FIf Amesbury is sent to prison or given
OL,7,Fa suspended sentence, he could face
OL,8,Fthe prospect of losing his seat in the
OL,9,FCommons.
OL,11,FA sentence of less than a year, even
OL,12,Fif it is suspended, would leave him
OL,13,Fliable to the recall process, which
OL,14,Fwould trigger a by-election if 10% of
OL,15,Fregistered voters in his seat sign a
OL,16,Fpetition calling for it.
OL,18,FA jail term of more than a year would
OL,19,Fmean Amesbury automatically losing his
OL,20,Fseat.
